            . I am servant to Mr. Parke, who lives in <placeName id="t18210214-113-crimeloc698">Cannonbury-place, Islington</placeName>
                  <interp inst="t18210214-113-crimeloc698" type="placeName" value="Cannonbury-place, Islington"></interp>
